        "# clean up data for BBall Ref\n",
        "\n",
        "df_br_2021_per36['MPG'] = df_br_2021_per36.apply(lambda row: row['MP'] / row['G'], axis = 1)\n",

        "\n",
        "df_br_2021_adv_pf = df_br_2021_adv.merge(df_br_2021_per36, how = 'inner')\n",
